videos.description: Seton Hall's Takal Molson throws up an alley-oop for Tyrese Samuel to throw down to complete the fast break.

tracking.trackingName: NCB_One-Play (Molson lobs to Samuel for Seton Hall fast-break dunk) 2020/12/04 ESHEET

videos.headline: Molson lobs to Samuel for Seton Hall fast-break dunk

videos.description: Ike Obiagu comes up with a monstrous block on the baseline, completely shutting down the layup attempt by Oregon's Eric Williams Jr.

tracking.trackingName: NCB_One-Play (Seton Hall's Ike Obiagu shuts down Oregon layup) 2020/12/04 ESHEET

videos.headline: Seton Hall's Ike Obiagu shuts down Oregon layup

videos.description: Myles Cale gets the steal and finds Jared Rhoden on the break with an alley-oop pass for an easy dunk finish on the fast break.

tracking.trackingName: NCB_One-Play (Cale's steal leads to Rhoden alley-oop dunk for Seton Hall) 2020/12/04 ESHEET

videos.headline: Cale's steal leads to Rhoden alley-oop dunk for Seton Hall
